# Patterns (regex) for URLs the link checker should skip.

# LinkedIn returns HTTP 999 to automated clients, so profile and newsletter
# links cannot be validated in CI. They are checked manually when added.
linkedin.com

# Microsoft Azure Local Solutions is a browser SPA with hash routes. The links
# work in browsers, but automated checks can receive 404 for the routed pages.
azurelocalsolutions\.azure\.microsoft\.com

# These sites are reachable in browsers, but currently reject or fail automated
# checks with 403/415/TLS/HTTP2 errors.
jakewalsh\.co\.uk/tag/azure-local
nmehelp\.getnerdio\.com/hc/en-us/articles/
www\.hpe\.com/psnow/doc/a50008245enw
www\.hpe\.com/us/en/alliance/microsoft/azurelocal\.html
